<P>
   (NYT31) SAN DIEGO -- Oct. 21, 1998 -- BBO-SERIES-WELLS-2, 10-21
-- A 1984 caricature of David Wells during his Toronto Blue Jays
days hangs at Cheswicks West, a bar in the San Diego neighborhood
of Ocean Beach. It is a ragged little beach neighborhood that dead
ends at the Pacific Ocean and is set apart from the hipper Pacific
Beach and upscale La Jolla by the San Diego River bed. Residents
say that living here is not just a lifestyle, it is an attitude.
(Robert Burroughs/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT30) SAN DIEGO -- Oct. 21, 1998 -- BBO-SERIES-WELLS-1, 10-21
-- Don Cameron, brother-in-law of David Wells, at Cheswicks West,
one of the Yankee pitcher's hangouts in the San Diego neighborhood
of Ocean Beach. ``Normally, when David's in town, we get together
in Ocean Beach, where he grew up,'' says Cameron. ``But, I think it
would have been too big a scene.'' Ocean Beach has remained much
the same as when Wells grew up there in the '70s and '80s. (Robert
Burroughs/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT29) SAN DIEGO -- Oct. 21, 1998 -- BBO-SERIES-4, 10-21 -- The
Padres' Kevin Brown pitching during the first inning Wednesday in
game 4 of the World Series between the Yankees and the Padres. With
a victory, the Yankees would sweep the series. (Barton
Silverman/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT28) HARTFORD, Conn. -- Oct. 21, 1998 -- SMART-GUNS-2, 10-21
-- Roydell Melbourne has been assembling Colt's pistols by hand for
33 years in Hartford. Colt's is hoping to perfect and market a new
generation of guns with technology that lets them be fired only by
their owner. (George Ruhe/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT27) ARVADA, Colo. -- Oct. 21, 1998 -- ENERGY-USE, 10-21 --
Michael and T.C. McCracken, along with their one-year-old daughter,
Lydia, outside their nearly completed home in Aryada, near Denver.
The McCrackens are far more willing than most Americans to conserve
energy. But standard features in their new home consume alot of
energy. (Ellen Jaskol/New York Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT26) SAN DIEGO -- Oct. 21, 1998 -- BBO-SERIES-3, 10-21 -- The
