 Updates to list cover review. 
 Editors: Following is a list of slugs and titles of the books
reviewed in the New York Times Book Review for Sunday Oct. 25.
<TEXT>
<P>
   ----------------------------------------------------
</P>
<P>
   ON THE COVER
</P>
<P>
   ----------------------------------------------------
</P>
<P>
   NYTBOOK-THOMAS-MORE-NYTSF, THE LIFE OF THOMAS MORE, By Peter
Ackroyd, Illustrated. 447 pp. New York: Nan A. Talese/Doubleday.
$30. Thomas More, this biography suggests, looked outside himself
to know why he had to die.
</P>
<P>
   --------------------------------------------------------
</P>
<P>
   FICTION
</P>
<P>
   --------------------------------------------------------
