Times of a Cultural Icon, By W. J. T. Mitchell, Illustrated. 321
pp. Chicago: The University of Chicago Press. $35. Does the
dinosaur stand for our collective political unconscious?
</P>
<P>
   NYTBOOK-RACE-NYTSF, THE SHAPE OF THE RIVER, Long-Term
