</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Buyer's edge: 10 get-now gifts for under $25
 &HT;    WITH PHOTOS
 &HT;    By Reagan Walker
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ATLANTA _ Before you can check it twice, you have to make your
list.
</P>
<P>
   Now's a good time.
</P>
<P>
   In fact, now is an excellent time to start your holiday shopping
and squirrel away some gifts.
</P>
<P>
   ``Once the Thanksgiving push comes, it's boom! You are in
competition with the world for the same item, the lines are long
and it's not as much fun,'' warns Atlantan Robyn Freedman Spizman,
author of ``The Perfect Present: The Ultimate Guide for Every
Occasion'' (Crown Publishers, $16). ``Now, you can find specials,
save money and put more thought into your presents.''
</P>
<P>
   To warm up, we suggest starting with those presents you know
you'll need _ to give hosts and hostesses, to stuff into stockings
and to pull out when that unexpected person arrives bearing a gift.
</P>
<P>
   We've done some early scouting for you and offer these ideas,
all of them under $25. So go ahead; get going. You'll thank us in
December.
</P>
<P>
   HOST AND HOSTESS GIFTS
</P>
<P>
   Candy wrap: Help the hostess save her party frock with this
candy-striped apron. It'll look perfect on him, too, at next
summer's backyard barbecue. One of many designs at the Rolling Pin
Kitchen Emporium in Gwinnett Place mall. 770-476-9275.(cq) $16.95.
Six metro locations.
</P>
<P>
   Now and later: A Christmas tree ornament immediately adds a
festive touch to the tree and the party and can also be enjoyed for
holidays to come. We found this iridescent beaded pear at
Gardentopia, 418 Church St., Decatur. 404-378-2929. $16.
</P>
<P>
   For the bar: For the thrill of the spill, a cocktail bar towel
comes in handy on the spot. Simply roll it up and tie it with a
ribbon and attach a gift card. We found this olive-green towel with
festive renditions of cocktails at Crate &AMP; Barrel at Perimeter
Mall. 770-671-9797. (cq) $7.95. Two metro locations.
</P>
<P>
   Other ideas for hosts and hostesses:
</P>
