<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-WIS-FEINGOLD-ART-2TAKES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
WISCONSIN RACE COULD BE DETERMINED BY KENTUCKY SENATOR 
</HEADLINE>
  (Duplication warning: Also filed in ``a'' category) 
(ART ADV: Photo is being sent to NYT photo clients. Non-subscribers
can make individual purchase by calling (888) 603-1036 or (888)
346-9867.) 
(mk) 
 By R.W. APPLE JR.   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
