<P>
   COMMUTER-FOLLIES (Los Angeles) _ Getting dressed. Flossing.
Putting on makeup and shaving. For thousands of Americans, these
are all part of the typical morning grind _ while driving. Many of
the 15,000 people who responded to an informal Pennzoil survey
admitted to doing a variety of personal chores while marooned in
rush-hour traffic. By David K. Baker. (Will move in the ``n''
