<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-22 21:33 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2449 &Cx1f; taf-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HOLD-LEIPZIG-MALL-NYT     10-22 0069
