   (NYT26) OFRA, West Bank -- Oct. 22, 1998 -- MIDEAST-REACT-2,
10-22 -- ``The Arabs will take over the land and come and go here
as they please,'' says Tali Hass, a settler shown in the window of
her mobile home in Ofra on the West Bank. Nevertheless, she hopes
to move to permanent housing in the settlement of 2,000 religious
Jews. (Rina Castelnuovo/New York Times Photo)
