<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    EDs: re-tops with Hussein joining talks, Palestinian charter;
updates throughout
 &HT;    CLINTON URGES MIDDLE EAST LEADERS: TRY TO MAINTAIN 'MOMENTUM OF
PEACE'
 &HT;    With ISRAEL-SETTLERS-1023; MIDEAST-BUDDY-1023.
